{"tid":108944,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"沙駕學車堂數問題","createTime":"2017-02-05T15:24:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-19T02:29:37.000Z","uid":9621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"99dc17574b075eea37102ca43df6dabe45a2b9bb","tid":108944,"uid":9621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T15:24:00.000Z","msg":"我五月中考車，但係個師傅1月頭已經約我，個師傅仲要約得好密，而家得返7節實習，1節獨立，1節模擬考試，同兩節長途<br />\n<br />\n我想知道係咪上得太快？如果補鍾既話有冇邊個師傅介紹？因為我唔想再係駕院補，好似貴好多<br />\n<br />\n如果出面補鍾既話係咪而家就要報名？之後駕院個留返2節就考之前一星期先上，1節考個日上<br />\n<br />\n我而家個情況好似唔太好咁，有冇三波想落二波會chok一下，起步有d慢，應該係摩擦點揾得唔好<br />\n<br />\nPS智專plan黎<br />\n<br />\n唔該巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06e436b948f152686939b7738bd675b559c661be","tid":108944,"uid":9621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T15:51:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"417f5a8ce4d92975b07873f542114e4e0ba74e8c","tid":108944,"uid":9621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T15:59:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0cf96fe3be95a414767c4c14096c0e6293468d23","tid":108944,"uid":47466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T16:10:42.000Z","msg":"好明顯太快啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5789e8afc56883577893c6d07a932a468b4907d","tid":108944,"uid":47466,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T16:15:35.000Z","msg":"我都係沙駕<br />\n我1上年9月尾考<br />\n8月先上第一堂<br />\n應該最後兩，三個月先上嫁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔好起駕院補3500 7堂on9既<br />\n<br />\n補堂既話<br />\n您一search 沙田補鐘就有<br />\n好似350一堂<br />\nd師傅會有禮貌d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申9月尾fail<br />\n下星期四補考<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n順帶一提<br />\n補考得7堂，我2月9考<br />\n2月5先上第一堂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n祝我好運"},{"pid":"ef83b5a8c32c6359a61affdadf00c0f13c569166","tid":108944,"uid":755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T17:01:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我五月中考車，但係個師傅1月頭已經約我，個師傅仲要約得好密，而家得返7節實習，1節獨立，1節模擬考試，同兩節長途<br />\n<br />\n我想知道係咪上得太快？如果補鍾既話有冇邊個師傅介紹？因為我唔想再係駕院補，好似貴好多<br />\n<br />\n如果出面補鍾既話係咪而家就要報名？之後駕院個留返2節就考之前一星期先上，1節考個日上<br />\n<br />\n我而家個情況好似唔太好咁，有冇三波想落二波會chok一下，起步有d慢，應該係摩擦點揾得唔好<br />\n<br />\nPS智專plan黎<br />\n<br />\n唔該巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都係三轉二chok"},{"pid":"d8e82c195c94a18975e96ca9a0aba2f75ba01d2d","tid":108944,"uid":755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T17:03:40.000Z","msg":"揸多幾次吊極力子就會熟練好多"},{"pid":"54fdc86d5064147ac0e6ca4e12efe595b1421aee","tid":108944,"uid":9621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T17:05:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好明顯太快啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唉，我都知架la<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12a170f3b4e6171234fc279f32261cdc32971040","tid":108944,"uid":9621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T17:14:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我都係沙駕<br />\n我1上年9月尾考<br />\n8月先上第一堂<br />\n應該最後兩，三個月先上嫁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔好起駕院補3500 7堂on9既<br />\n<br />\n補堂既話<br />\n您一search 沙田補鐘就有<br />\n好似350一堂<br />\nd師傅會有禮貌d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申9月尾fail<br />\n下星期四補考<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n順帶一提<br />\n補考得7堂，我2月9考<br />\n2月5先上第一堂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n祝我好運</blockquote><br />\n我就係見到有好多補鍾，但係唔知邊間好，巴打講350係兩節？因為我見學車易係5000蚊有20節（10堂）<br />\n<br />\n巴打祝你好運，考車我成日覺得好睇運，唔好比咁大壓力自己<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nBTW如果决定左出面補鍾，係咪同學院導師講淨係練乙部試，唔好出街練？"},{"pid":"85236d408518ff1091906ab47263f0a3cbf6e04a","tid":108944,"uid":9621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T17:16:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我五月中考車，但係個師傅1月頭已經約我，個師傅仲要約得好密，而家得返7節實習，1節獨立，1節模擬考試，同兩節長途<br />\n<br />\n我想知道係咪上得太快？如果補鍾既話有冇邊個師傅介紹？因為我唔想再係駕院補，好似貴好多<br />\n<br />\n如果出面補鍾既話係咪而家就要報名？之後駕院個留返2節就考之前一星期先上，1節考個日上<br />\n<br />\n我而家個情況好似唔太好咁，有冇三波想落二波會chok一下，起步有d慢，應該係摩擦點揾得唔好<br />\n<br />\nPS智專plan黎<br />\n<br />\n唔該巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都係三轉二chok</blockquote><br />\n我有朋友話踩break踩到1000轉左右再落波就唔會chok<br />\n<br />\n我呀sir成日叫我落左波之後呼一下油，我夠知真係出街揸既話會順d la，但係一陣考試我呼多左咪仲chok"},{"pid":"d4e04f1b3e687935d562b3c30627a546485e83b9","tid":108944,"uid":9621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T17:17:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>揸多幾次吊極力子就會熟練好多</blockquote><br />\n我都希望係，我成日吊得唔夠高<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7ed9dda6d2f377af1b178b488e2246f4a055a00","tid":108944,"uid":9621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T17:18:05.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">有冇巴打可以介紹補鍾比我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></span>"},{"pid":"e86c08f9653077f022a99ab11058cd745b6b9ee4","tid":108944,"uid":35506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T17:19:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我五月中考車，但係個師傅1月頭已經約我，個師傅仲要約得好密，而家得返7節實習，1節獨立，1節模擬考試，同兩節長途<br />\n<br />\n我想知道係咪上得太快？如果補鍾既話有冇邊個師傅介紹？因為我唔想再係駕院補，好似貴好多<br />\n<br />\n如果出面補鍾既話係咪而家就要報名？之後駕院個留返2節就考之前一星期先上，1節考個日上<br />\n<br />\n我而家個情況好似唔太好咁，有冇三波想落二波會chok一下，起步有d慢，應該係摩擦點揾得唔好<br />\n<br />\nPS智專plan黎<br />\n<br />\n唔該巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n3轉2 唔好一下放哂離合<br />\n應該放到磨擦點 再慢慢放<br />\n<br />\nps岩岩pass 冇耐<br />\n<br />\n有錯指點下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7f42cba5aae861ed8e476c7e79582b8c77ee57c","tid":108944,"uid":81569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T17:21:15.000Z","msg":"其實係咪好多人報左駕院課程，再自己出去找街外師傅補鐘？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c1ddb77e6bfe4c6a9941982400c8922b4a1f295","tid":108944,"uid":47466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T17:27:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">有冇巴打可以介紹補鍾比我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></span></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n您搵搵<br />\neric<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢有得比您免費睇堂<br />\n您覺得ok先學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2ed3b811a7a8c0bde29ed0eb59f9dc01cd5dc3f","tid":108944,"uid":47466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T17:28:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實係咪好多人報左駕院課程，再自己出去找街外師傅補鐘？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n因為學院d人太hae<br />\n做唔做都收咁多人工"},{"pid":"ba8ed99f9dd9a6146624be29f6ef83abf8e09401","tid":108944,"uid":70689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T17:43:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\n我而家個情況好似唔太好咁，有冇三波想落二波會chok一下，起步有d慢，應該係摩擦點揾得唔好<br />\n</blockquote><br />\n三波落二波<br />\n想唔chok就先收慢(印象中30km-25km左右)<br />\n然後先落二波 慢放極力子<br />\n<br />\n起步慢<br />\n留意交通燈<br />\n行人綠公仔閃緊<br />\n你就入定一波準備吊極力子<br />\n綠燈就可以鬆手掣"},{"pid":"9be6f90703b388c2cf4868bd3f94e16f466392ca","tid":108944,"uid":9621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T00:45:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">有冇巴打可以介紹補鍾比我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></span></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n您搵搵<br />\neric<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢有得比您免費睇堂<br />\n您覺得ok先學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n而個我都見到有，巴打係佢學生？覺得點？"},{"pid":"988b43c3d5faa269065b889158186993d37bb8e1","tid":108944,"uid":9621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T00:46:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><br />\n我而家個情況好似唔太好咁，有冇三波想落二波會chok一下，起步有d慢，應該係摩擦點揾得唔好<br />\n</blockquote><br />\n三波落二波<br />\n想唔chok就先收慢(印象中30km-25km左右)<br />\n然後先落二波 慢放極力子<br />\n<br />\n起步慢<br />\n留意交通燈<br />\n行人綠公仔閃緊<br />\n你就入定一波準備吊極力子<br />\n綠燈就可以鬆手掣</blockquote><br />\n唔該巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79738fd9675f97b76ee84d3dabdd09d1de8ff1a7","tid":108944,"uid":9621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T05:49:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf8b7e662d718c77477342f550612ead699b355b","tid":108944,"uid":9621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T05:49:51.000Z","msg":"有冇沙駕師傅介紹"},{"pid":"311edb5b45865126c99a2ae5c8d2aeb0ddaefd43","tid":108944,"uid":47466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T05:52:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">有冇巴打可以介紹補鍾比我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></span></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n您搵搵<br />\neric<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢有得比您免費睇堂<br />\n您覺得ok先學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n而個我都見到有，巴打係佢學生？覺得點？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我跟佢車一次<br />\n教得唔錯<br />\n佢後尾比左另一個師傅我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n都教得唔錯"},{"pid":"b6791fd255446d5834765fd767b99cd0034a4c50","tid":108944,"uid":9621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T05:56:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><span style=\"font-size: x-